<h4>Session Workflow</h4>
<p>Every session moves through three stages. Each stage can only move forward — it cannot go back.</p>
<ol>
    <li>
        <strong>Opened</strong> — the session is created and scheduled.
        Equipment setup and preparation notes can be entered.
        <em>(Owner, Administration, or Trainer)</em>
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Logged</strong> — exercises and SOAP notes have been recorded
        after the appointment takes place.
        <em>(Owner or Trainer)</em>
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Completed</strong> — admin review is finished and payment is confirmed.
        This is the final stage.
        <em>(Owner or Administration)</em>
    </li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Canceled</strong> — future Opened sessions can be canceled by an Owner or Administration with a required reason. Canceled sessions are automatically archived.</p>
